Bc5 18. c4 O-O 19. cxd5 exd5 $11) 15... Qb7 16. c4 d5 17. cxd5 exd5 18. Qb3
Ndc5 19. Qxd5 Qxd5 20. Nc7+ Kd7 21. Nxd5 Bd6 {The d3-pawn is a serious asset
